The '''''Rampart''-class anticoncussion generator''' was a type of [[anticoncussion field]] generator.

==History==
The ''Rampart''-class anticoncussion generator was used in the [[Stars' End/Legends|Stars' End]] [[Prison/Legends|prison]] on [[Mytus VII/Legends|Mytus VII]] to supplement the structure's [[molecularly bonded armor]]. It absorbed and dispersed kinetic energy, neutralizing blasts, collisions, and impacts. The system consumed an enormous amount of energy, on par with that used by a [[Star Destroyer/Legends|Star Destroyer's]] [[Ion engine/Legends|ion engine]].<ref name="EGWT">''[[The Essential Guide to Weapons and Technology]]''</ref>

